\/Perfect-Scrambled-Eggs-600x302.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/Perfect-Scrambled-Eggs-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/>Whatever your budget and choice the team at Red Radish will make sure everyone feels happy and <a title=\"Navigating Craft Sevices\" href=\"http:\/\/www.theblackandblue.com\/2011\/02\/04\/7-tips-for-navigating-craft-services-successfully\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>well catered for<\/strong><\/a> at the end of every day. Quite simply we just would not take the job unless we could deliver the goods and the smiles! Poor quality catering and craft services is the single biggest source of complaints on any given production, so producers and production companies will often spend a lot of time and effort looking for a top-notch caterer and craft service company like us. But like all businesses and within any price range, there are better and worse catering companies for the job so just be careful of who you choose and make sure you always take out a few references from <a title=\"Customer References\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/category\/customer-references\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>past satisfied clients.<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p>This is our basic list but obviously it can be adjusted to suit all budget and dietary requirments!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Breakfast\/Call time<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">\u00a0Selection of Mini Croissants and Pastries<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Homemade Mini Breakfast Muffins<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Homemade Mini Sausage Rolls<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Free- range Scrambled Eggs<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Selection of Bread<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Slices of Ham<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2381\" title=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/sweet-jars-craft-services.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/sweet-jars-craft-services.jpg 960w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/sweet-jars-craft-services-600x236.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/sweet-jars-craft-services-300x118.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Craft Menu All Day<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">\u00a0Nespresso of freshly brewed Coffee and Cappuccinos<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Regular Tea and Herbal Teas<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Orange Juice and Bottled Water<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Fresh Fruit Basket<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Fruit Platters<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Freshly Cut Vegetables and dips<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Mints and Chewing Gum<\/p>\n<p align=\"center\">Selection of Sweets and Chocolates<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fresh lemon and Ginger<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">Dried Fruits and Nuts<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">Basic First Aid Kit<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hand Sanitiser<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">And wherever Possible &#8211; Newspapers and Fresh Flowers<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2491\" title=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/newspapers-flowers-craft-services-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/newspapers-flowers-craft-services-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/newspapers-flowers-craft-services-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/01\/newspapers-flowers-craft-services.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"auto, (ma